  fixed background colour (#12191A) so the heavily overlapped layers still read as three steps.
  Sized (24 units, offset 12) to keep the whole diagonal inside the 66dp safe circle.
  Ramp bottom->top: #2F5D62 deep teal (heatmap teal), #7FB2B7 light teal, #E8B75D amber.
-->
